*Znaju* da se moraš truditi da bi uspeo. (They know that you have to work hard to succeed.)

Umeju *znaju* da postignu svoje ciljeve. (They are able to achieve their goals.)

Oni *znaju* kako da se snalaze u svim situacijama. (They know how to cope in all situations.)

Većina ljudi *znaju* da je dobro biti dobar prema drugima. (Most people know that it is good to be kind to others.)

Često se *znaju* iznenaditi kad čuju nove vesti. (They often get surprised when they hear new news.)

Čak i deca *znaju* da je bitno da poštuju tuđa mišljenja. (Even children know that it is important to respect other people's opinions.)